>>> <eqenchanters-owner@onelist.com> 04/19 2:53 PM >>>
From: eqenchanters-owner@...

Hello,

There is a new survey for the eqenchanters community.

I was just wondering what other people had chosen, so I'm sending out this survey. I'm not sure if some of the choices I put here are really able to be enchanters, but I guess I'll find out.
What race is your enchanter?

----

Possible answers are:

o Human
o Half-Elf
o High Elf
o Wood Elf
o Erudite
o Dark Elf
o Dwarf
o Gnome
o Halfling


To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://www.onelist.com/surveycenter/eqenchanters


Thanks!

eqenchanters Owner
